Using: RC2 

I loaded some porjects from my repository.  I fixed a classpath problem on the 
java build property page of one of the projects - a classpath variable was not 
present in my workspace so I removed the jar files and added them using the 
ECLIPSE_HOME variable instead.  Then I hit OK.  At the end of the build I got a 
warning dialog that said Error Setting Build Path.  The message was "An error 
occured while setting the build path.  Reason: Errors during build."  In the 
details area was the following:
  Null argument; Do not have resource info for resource in delta.
